    "# üèÄ NBA API Historical Data Fetcher - Adjusted for Max Accuracy\n",
    "\n",
    "**Adjusted Version:** Added live daily updates, merge with 10-year CSVs, and quantum-inspired ensembles (average multiple fetches with noise) to handle uncertainty and keep the quantum vibe.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Purpose:** Fetch thousands of historical NBA games for QEPC backtesting\n",
    "\n",
    "**What this does:**\n",
    "- Downloads games from multiple NBA seasons with live updates\n",
    "- Processes data into QEPC-compatible format\n",
    "- Merges with your existing 10-year CSVs\n",
    "- Gives you 5,000+ games for backtesting!\n",
    "\n",
    "**Time:** ~10-15 minutes to run\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
